    • convertPointsToGPoints

      public static java.util.List<Intersectable.GeoPoint> convertPointsToGPoints​(Geometry shape, java.util.List<Point3D> points)
      Useful function mainly for the Geometry that implements findIntersection() method which in their test, dealing with comparison between List and List. It's even more useful due to the ability to send every Geometry type object and activating the polymorphism to get it.
      Parameters:
      shape - in order to convert Point3D to GeoPoints we need to determine the sort of the shape
      points - the list of the points which we need to convert into List
      Returns:
      List
